555
00:39:47,310 --> 00:39:50,650
even though she knows all about our relationship and plans.

556
00:39:53,970 --> 00:39:56,330
Oppa, you're not...

557
00:39:56,610 --> 00:39:59,710
hoping it isn't Ji Hyun, are you?

558
00:39:59,990 --> 00:40:01,900
