559
00:40:02,880 --> 00:40:05,620
Because it can't be Ji Hyun.

560
00:40:05,940 --> 00:40:09,710
If it's true that Ji Hyun's soul is in Song Yi Kyung's body,

561
00:40:09,860 --> 00:40:11,940
