Ji Hyun!

590
00:43:16,170 --> 00:43:18,040
Ji Hyun!

591
00:43:33,580 --> 00:43:35,360
Dad!

592
00:43:35,930 --> 00:43:37,410
Dad!

593
00:43:38,950 --> 00:43:41,220
He woke up!

594
00:43:41,400 --> 00:43:44,290
My dad woke up!

595
00:43:44,890 --> 00:43:47,050
