death schedule every ten days.

614
00:45:06,350 --> 00:45:08,330
I'm a low-level scheduler.

615
00:45:08,390 --> 00:45:09,870
Right.

616
00:45:10,060 --> 00:45:12,440
When I first met you,

617
00:45:12,520 --> 00:45:15,760
